      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Andrew Fan</b>\n</p><p><b>Andrew Fan</b>,<br />\na British software development engineer, M.Sc. in CS from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Essex\">University of Essex</a> in 1994, and former <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Systems_analyst\">system analyst</a> at <a href=\"/index.php?title=Motorola&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Motorola (page does not exist)\">Motorola</a> Semiconductors <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hong_Kong\">Hong Kong</a> Ltd. <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nAs computer chess programmer, Andrew is author of the chess engines <a href=\"/index.php?title=KKFChess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"KKFChess (page does not exist)\">KKFChess</a> and <a href=\"/FireFly\" title=\"FireFly\">FireFly</a>. He is further involved in the <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallel search</a> framework of <a href=\"/Dirty\" title=\"Dirty\">Dirty</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and has written the <a href=\"/TLCS-TLCV\" title=\"TLCS-TLCV\">TLCS/TLCV</a> clients WBROG and REGO <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Fan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47605\">New chess engine - FireFly 1.0.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Fan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 18, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47717\">KKFChess 2.6.3 and FireFly 1.0.2 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Fan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 30, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=50616&amp;p=192200\">32-bit Magic experiments</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Fan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, December 03, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a>, <a href=\"/Kindergarten_Bitboards\" title=\"Kindergarten Bitboards\">Kindergarten Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Fan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrew-fan-83956124/\">Andrew Fan | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://fireflychess.dyndns.pro/JQuery/FF_JQ_UI.html\">FireFly's Home page</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Fan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrew-fan-83956124/\">Andrew Fan | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerschaak.nl/index.php/nieuws/51-toernooien/692-48th-pt-2015-leiden-list-of-participants-2\">48th PT 2015 Leiden: List of participants</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20171016195126/http://fireflychess.dyndns.pro/JQuery/FF_JQ_UI.html\">FireFly's Home page including WBROG and REGO</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, 2017)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301154041\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6884-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301154041 and revision id 18069\n -->\n"
